each of these config keys should be wrapped in an if to only be rendered when they are set and in tandem make the default value  in config.yaml empty.

{%- if mnesia_table_loading_retry_timeout %}
    {mnesia_table_loading_retry_timeout, {{ mnesia_table_loading_retry_timeout }}},
